      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·魚藻之什·007.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">黍苗.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>芃芃黍苗，陰雨膏之。悠悠南行，召伯勞之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Tall and strong grows the young millet,
Fattened by the genial rains.
Very long was our journey to the south,
But the earl of Zhou encouraged and cheered us.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-yuzao-007__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
