      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·魚藻之什·007.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">黍苗.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>我徒我御，我師我旅。我行既集，蓋云歸處。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>We went along on foot; we rode in our chariots; --
Our whole host, and our battalions.
When our expedition was accomplished,
We knew we should return home.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
