      <prop type="x-translation-ref">黍苗.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>肅肅謝功，召伯營之。烈烈征師，召伯成之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Severe was the work at Su,
But the earl of Zhou built the city.
Majestic was the march of our host; --
The earl of Zhou directed it.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
