      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·魚藻之什·007.5</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">黍苗.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>原隰既平，泉流既清。召伯有成，王心則寧。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The plains and low lands were regulated; --
The springs and streams were cleared.
The earl of Zhou completed his work,
And the heart of the king was at rest.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
